02:34.020 --> 02:35.648
<i>Kee oth rama pancake!</i>

02:35.722 --> 02:36.722
<i>Aaaaaaaargh!</i>

02:36.789 --> 02:38.724
- Whoa!
- Geez Louise!

02:38.791 --> 02:40.453
<i>The dungeon's 80
paces west of here</i>

02:40.527 --> 02:42.155
<i>under a dumb-looking rock.</i>

02:42.228 --> 02:44.163
<i>And, Finn, this dungeon's
