03:08.922 --> 03:10.720
Yeah, yeah, yeah!

03:11.925 --> 03:14.360
- Wait, Jake!
- But... burgers and hot dogs.

03:14.427 --> 03:17.693
Didn't you say you were hungry
for burgers this <i>morning?</i>

03:17.764 --> 03:18.629
Yeah. So?

03:18.698 --> 03:21.065
