burgers and hot dogs

03:24.537 --> 03:26.699
are burgers and hot dogs at all.

03:29.709 --> 03:31.644
Aaaaaaaaaaah...

03:31.711 --> 03:32.711
Boom!!

03:48.127 --> 03:49.720
Yaaaaaaah!

03:49.796 --> 03:51.924
Ew.

03:51.998 --> 03:53.227
Duhhh.

03:55.602 --> 03:57.662
Hyah!

04:00.840 --> 04:02.138
Ahhhh.

04:02.208 --> 04:03.870
Dude!

04:03.943 --> 04:05.935
Look!

04:08.815 --> 04:10.340
<i>Finn, cover up those
nubs on your head.</i>

04:10.416 --> 04:12.715
Man, again?

04:12.785 --> 04:15.721
<i>All right, Jake, I wanna remind
you what this dungeon's for.</i>

04:15.788 --> 04:18.154
<i>In order for Finn
to stop whining,</i>

04:18.224 --> 04:20.216
<i>he needs to be put
through a trial</i>

04:20.293 --> 04:22.093
<i>that forces him to take
charge of a situation.</i>

04:22.161 --> 04:24.562
But, Dad, Finn's already
figured that out.

04:24.631 --> 04:26.327
He's a good kid
with a kind heart.

04:26.399 --> 04:28.994
<i>Remember, Jake, this is a
pre-recorded holo-message.</i>

04:29.068 --> 04:31.046
<i>I can't hear you if you're
talking to me right now.</i>

04:31.070 --> 04:32.834
I'm gonna go walk around!

04:32.905 --> 04:34.669
Okay!

04:34.741 --> 04:36.175
<i>Jake, I need your help.</i>

04:36.242 --> 04:37.676
<i>You got to call
Finn a whiny baby.</i>

04:37.744 --> 04:39.337
- But...
<i>- Butts are for pooping.</i>

04:39.412 --> 04:40.971
<i>Do it for Poppy.</i>

04:42.015 --> 04:45.179
Finn?! - Over here!

04:45.251 --> 04:47.777
Check it out, Jake.
I found two ways.

04:47.854 --> 04:50.119
This way has some
kind of flower trap,

04:50.189 --> 04:52.920
and that way... has <i>that</i> guy.

04:52.992 --> 04:55.985
None shall pa-a-a-a-ss!

04:56.062 --> 04:58.497
Ugh! Let's take the flower path.

04:58.564 --> 04:59.862
Mm.

04:59.932 --> 05:03.767
Wait! Why don't you
want to take <i>my</i> path?

05:03.836 --> 05:06.533
Because you're super gross, man.

05:06.606 --> 05:07.606
Oh.

05:09.142 --> 05:10.269
Cheer up, man.

05:10.343 --> 05:12.621
We're only telling you you're
gross because we're your bros.

05:12.645 --> 05:13.738
Really?

05:13.813 --> 05:16.078
Yeah. Bros are real
with each other.

05:16.149 --> 05:18.675
And you're gross, brother.
Take a bath.

05:18.751 --> 05:20.481
Thanks, brother.

05:20.553 --> 05:22.545
No probs.

05:23.956 --> 05:25.390
Hey, what did Dad say?

05:25.458 --> 05:28.053
Um...

05:28.127 --> 05:30.062
He said he's surprised
a whiny baby like you

05:30.129 --> 05:31.620
made it this far.

05:31.698 --> 05:34.361
What? Why's Dad
saying all that jive?

05:34.434 --> 05:35.868
Mrnh.

05:35.935 --> 05:38.029
<i>Jake, do it for Poppy!</i>

05:40.106 --> 05:44.168
Because you cry
like a baby, baby!

05:44.243 --> 05:47.407
Dude, you're picking on me, too?

05:50.016 --> 05:52.713
Whoa.

05:55.822 --> 05:57.450
I don't even cry much.

05:57.523 --> 06:00.049
I only cry when it's healthy,
like when people die.

06:00.126 --> 06:03.221
Partake of the fruit.

06:03.296 --> 06:04.855
Pfth! Blech! Ugh.

06:04.931 --> 06:06.331
If I didn't cry
when people died,

06:06.399 --> 06:07.890
I'd have a cold
butt for a heart.

06:07.967 --> 06:11.096
The fru-u... u-it.

06:11.170 --> 06:14.106
"Waaaah! I cry when people die!

06:14.173 --> 06:16.142
Waaaah! I'm Finn!"

06:16.209 --> 06:18.838
Partake of the fruit.

06:18.911 --> 06:21.005
Maybe I <i>will</i> partake
of the fruit!

06:21.080 --> 06:23.106
Yeah! Yeah! Yeah! Yeah, fruit!

06:23.182 --> 06:25.117
- Dude, don't eat that!
- Why not?

06:25.184 --> 06:27.119
All the people that I
care about in this world

06:27.186 --> 06:29.781
are being wads. - Ohh...

06:29.856 --> 06:33.258
<i>Don't you blow Poppy's cover!</i>

06:33.326 --> 06:37.491
N-o-o-o-o-o-o-o-o-o-o!

06:42.135 --> 06:44.127
Whoa.

06:50.710 --> 06:54.977
Time to go, baby.

06:55.047 --> 06:56.777
Finn, come on!

06:56.849 --> 06:59.284
I'm gonna hang here
with these fruit babes.

06:59.352 --> 07:01.480
<i>They'll</i> be my best buds now.

07:01.554 --> 07:03.182
Yah!

07:26.312 --> 07:27.905
There's another cartridge!

07:27.980 --> 07:33.749
Pbffffffffffffffffffft!

07:33.820 --> 07:36.585
All right, man, Dad told me
not to tell you this, but...

07:36.656 --> 07:38.318
<i>Don't tell him!</i>

07:38.391 --> 07:40.622
You're not real.

07:44.897 --> 07:46.490
Dad asked me to call you "baby"

07:46.566 --> 07:48.034
