the fruit witches.</i>

08:09.155 --> 08:12.216
<i>Hey, did they make you
cry, Finn, huh? Huh?</i>

08:12.291 --> 08:14.021
<i>I bet they did.</i>

08:14.093 --> 08:16.324
<i>All right. Now cover
your ears, Sue.</i>

08:16.395 --> 08:18.193
